      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be completely transparent about what you're getting. The exterior has sustained significant damage \u2014 deep scratches, multiple dents, and substantial paint fading and chipping across several panels. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn or heavily worn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this vehicle has known issues that will require attention, and we strongly recommend a full inspection by a qualified mechanic before purchase. This car is best suited for a buyer who is comfortable with a project vehicle or is looking for parts. It is priced accordingly to reflect its current state, and we believe it represents a fair opportunity for the right buyer willing to put in the work.",
